idle_timeout.gcode:
TURN_OFF_HEATERS
M84
M107
G4 P20000
SET_LED LED=led_strip WHITE=0.0
G4 P500
POWER_OFF_PRINTER

gcode_macro M600.gcode:
{% set X = 110 %}
{% set Y = 0 %}


SET_FILAMENT_SENSOR SENSOR=e0_sensor ENABLE=0
PAUSE
G91
G1 E-.8 F2700

G90
G1 X{X} Y{Y} F3000
G91
G1 E-100 F1000
{ action_respond_info("Filament change, resume after.") }
